data.meta_description: CV Civil & Structural Head-O.RAJEH  - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. Rajeh Oussama is a Tunisian civil engineer born in 1985. He has worked as a study engineer, project engineer, and project manager for various companies since 2010. His responsibilities have included structural design, project management, and engineering work for industrial facilities. He is currently a study/project engineer at P.I.R.E.C.O where he performs civil/structural engineering and prepares technical proposals, specifications, and designs.
